Currency Derivatives

 

Map of the Market


The Market Map is mosaic plot of tiled color-coded data cluster which differentiates performances of each sector in an index. 
							It provides an edge in identifying critical issues, comprehending emerging trends and viewing complex market performances at multiple levels in a comprehensive manner.
Map of the Market
 
TAME Charts


TAME(Technical Analysis Made Easy) is a charting technique and analysis tool to measure market movements with the help of indicators. TAME provides an exhilarating experience with its inbuilt indicators that make analysis simple and easy. 
Charts
 
