Historical Trade data
Historical high frequency tick by tick trades data is provided through internet download facility. The historical data is available for the Capital Market Segment, Futures & Option Segment and Wholesale Debt Market Segment. Historical Data contains (a) Day wise bhavcopy for each trading day, (b) Circulars issued by NSE or NSCCL during the month, (c) Masters containing information like symbols, series, ISINs etc., (d) Snapshots of the limit order book at four time points in the day and (e) Trades data containing details about every trade that took place.
