Corporate Data
Corporate Data contains data pertaining to company fundamentals, corporate announcements and shareholding pattern. This data is provided on-line through a dedicated 2 mbps channelised E1 private leased line circuit. The cost of subscription of this data is Rs. 10,00,000 per annum.
